snippet.title: Enders Gate TCG Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to dive into the world of Enders Gate, the newest and most exciting web3 Trading Card Game (TCG) on the block! With over 300 collectible digital trading cards featuring stunning hand-drawn art from artists around the world, the possibilities are endless. Create and customize your own decks with 25-30 cards and put your skills to the test in epic card battles against other players. Will you emerge victorious? Join Enders Gate and find out!

Join our discord for details: 
https://discord.gg/endersgate
